<html metal:use-macro="here/@@standard_macros/master">
  <head>
    <title metal:fill-slot="title"
           tal:content="string:Privacy - ${view/portal_title}" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div metal:fill-slot="content">
      <div id="oc-content-main">
        <div class="oc-headingBlock">
          <h1 tal:content="string:About ${view/portal_title}" />
        </div>
        <p>OpenPlans aims to transform social activism by providing tools that connect people and enable them to share ideas, stay organized, and act collectively to effect change.</p>
        
        <h1>About <acronym title="The Open Planning Project">TOPP</acronym></h1>
        <p>OpenPlans is the work of <a href="http://topp.openplans.org/">The Open Planning Project</a>, a New York City-based non-profit organization dedicated to using technology to enhance community participation. In addition to OpenPlans, we also sponsor <a href="http://www.geoserver.org/">GeoServer</a>, an open source platform for sharing geographic information, and the <a href="http://www.nycsr.org/">New York City Streets Renaissance Campaign</a>, which advocates for lively public space in New York City.</p>
      </div><!-- content-main -->
      <div id="oc-content-sidebar">
        <div id="oc-contact" class="oc-boxy">
          <h2>Contact Us</h2>
            <address class="vcard">
              <p style="font-weight: bold;" class="fn org">
                <a class="url" href="http://topp.openplans.org">The Open Planning Project</a>
              </p>
              <dl class="oc-plainList">
                <dt>Address</dt>
                <dd class="adr">
                  <div class="street-address">349 West 12th Street #3</div>
                  <span class="locality">New York</span>, <span class="region">NY</span> <span class="postal-code">10014</span>
                </dd>
                <dt>Phone</dt>
                <dd class="tel">212.219.6070</dd>
                <dt>Fax</dt>
                <dd class="tel">646.390.2624</dd>
                <dt>Email (General Inquiries)</dt>
                <dd class="email"
                    tal:content="structure python:view.spamProtect('info@openplans.org')" />
                <dt>Email (Help)</dt>
                <dd class="email"
                    tal:content="structure python:view.spamProtect('help@openplans.org')" />
              </dl>
            </address>
        </div>
        <div class="oc-boxy">
          <h2>Help!</h2>
          <p>
            We are here for you. If you could use some help, don't hesitate
            to email <span tal:replace="python:view.spamProtect('help@openplans.org')" />
            or visit the <a style="" href="http://www.openplans.org/projects/openplans-help/">OpenPlans Help and Documentation</a> project.
            If you have technical knowledge and want to get involved, 
            visit the <a style="" href="http://www.openplans.org/projects/opencore/">OpenCore Software</a> project for more information.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div><!-- content-fill-slot -->
  </body>
</html>
